			Oh goodness, this sounds (and looks) so delicious.  Normally, frosting isn&#039;t my thing.  It has to be super light for me to enjoy it.  Most of the time it&#039;s just to heavy and too sweet (if that&#039;s possible) for me to enjoy.  I&#039;m going to have to try this ASAP.  I&#039;d definitely do it this weekend, but it is hubs birthday and I&#039;ve already picked out a reese&#039;s peanut butter cup cake to make him.			<div class="clr"></div>
