			<h4>
				pattyk <span>on Tuesday, March 16</span>
			</h4>
			This is the traditional Red Velvet Cake frosting we have always used, and is much better than cream cheese frosting that most people use on Red Velvet.  It is much better if each layer of cake is split and also much prettier.  Refrigerate the cake or the frosting will not taste as good after a few days.			<div class="clr"></div>
			<p></p>

